HEADWORD: Nontronite
<hw>Non"tro*nite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[So called
because found in the arrondissement of <etsep>Nontron</etsep>,
France.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A greenish yellow or green
mineral, consisting chiefly of the hydrous silicate of iron.</def>⟦br⟧
